videos.headline: Lindsay breaks loose for 39-yard gain.
videos.description: Phillip Lindsay gets up field for a 39-yard gain to the redone for Colorado.

videos.headline: Montez finds Ross for a 22 yard TD
videos.description: Steven Montez connects with Devin Ross across the middle for the 22- yard touchdown.

videos.headline: Wharton III shows off his arm with a 15-yard TD pass to Kanawai Noa.
videos.description: Vic Wharton III gets a fly sweep hand off and throws to Kanawai Noa for a 15- yard touchdown.

videos.headline: Montez throws deep to Shenault Jr. for 58-yard gain
videos.description: Steven Montez connects with Laviska Shenault Jr. for a deep 58-yard strike.

videos.headline: Montez keeps it and runs in for the 7-yard TD
videos.description: Steven Montez calls his own number and runs in untouched for a 7-yard touchdown.

videos.headline: Bowers comes up with the tough grab for a 27-yard TD
videos.description: Ross Bowers lobs it up to Kanawai Noa who makes a difficult catch for the 27-yard touchdown.

videos.headline: Noyer fumbles snap on 4th and short and CAL'S Looney recovers it
videos.description: Sam Noyer mishandles the snap and James Looney is there to  recover the fumble for the Cal Bears.

videos.headline: Montez connects with MacIntyre for 4th TD of the day
videos.description: Steven Montez gets 4th touchdown of the day finding Jay MacIntyre for a 23-yard touchdown pass.

videos.headline: Bowers finds Wharton III across the middle for 14-yard TD
videos.description: Ross Bowers connects with Vic Wharton III for the second time for a 14-yard touchdown.
